    {
        "line_number": 2,
        "text": "(३) भोजन व शरीर पुष्ट रखनेका बयान।।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/simha1914_03_textline_2.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 139,
            "y1": 371,
            "x2": 1989,
            "y2": 535
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 3,
        "text": "सर्वदा अच्छे २ भोजनसे शरीर तो पुष्ट होताहै,",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/simha1914_03_textline_3.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 257,
            "y1": 510,
            "x2": 1974,
            "y2": 672
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 4,
        "text": "परन्तु आत्माको कुछ सुख नहीं होता; आत्मिक सुख",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/simha1914_03_textline_4.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 139,
            "y1": 674,
            "x2": 1982,
            "y2": 823
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 5,
        "text": "परोपकारसेही होताहै. अपनी तारीफ़ आप न करना",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/simha1914_03_textline_5.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 145,
            "y1": 818,
            "x2": 1979,
            "y2": 973
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 6,
        "text": "चाहिये, अगर तारीफ़ लायक़ गुण है तो हरएक तारीफ़",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/simha1914_03_textline_6.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 142,
            "y1": 970,
            "x2": 1977,
            "y2": 1119
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 7,
        "text": "करेंगे. अपने मुंह मियांमिट्ठू बनना मूर्खता है,जब कि",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/simha1914_03_textline_7.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 121,
            "y1": 1109,
            "x2": 1984,
            "y2": 1275
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 8,
        "text": "दो मनुष्य बातें करतेहैं तो बिना बुलाये न जाना न",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/simha1914_03_textline_8.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 142,
            "y1": 1266,
            "x2": 1982,
            "y2": 1428
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 9,
        "text": "छिपकर सुनना चाहिये; इसमें अपनी निन्दा होतीहै.",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/simha1914_03_textline_9.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 142,
            "y1": 1409,
            "x2": 1976,
            "y2": 1569
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 10,
        "text": "यदि तुम कोई बात कहना चाहतेहो और सुननेवाले",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/simha1914_03_textline_10.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 134,
            "y1": 1561,
            "x2": 1982,
            "y2": 1717
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 11,
        "text": "का मन नहीं लगता तो चुप रहना अच्छाहै. जो काम",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/simha1914_03_textline_11.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 129,
            "y1": 1713,
            "x2": 1979,
            "y2": 1863
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 12,
        "text": "तुमसे न होसके तो उसमें हाथ डालकर अपनी हँसी",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/simha1914_03_textline_12.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 131,
            "y1": 1862,
            "x2": 1992,
            "y2": 2011
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 13,
        "text": "मत करावो. हमेशा बुराइयोंसे बचना, साफ़ पानी पीना",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/simha1914_03_textline_13.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 134,
            "y1": 2011,
            "x2": 1995,
            "y2": 2163
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 14,
        "text": "और प्रतिदिन दो तीन मील भ्रमण करना चाहिये.",
